high_descs: Turn to the right and face the bath tub and look up.
Pick up the toilet paper from the toilet tank.
Carry the toilet paper and turn around, then left. Turn left to face the sink.
Place the toilet paper on the toilet paper holder, to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move toilet paper to the holder.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the left side of the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper on the toilet tank.
Place the toilet paper roll on the toilet paper hook.
anns.task_desc: Place a toilet paper roll on a toilet paper hook.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper from the top of the toilet.
Turn right and walk to the other side of the toilet.
Put the toilet paper on the toilet paper holder near the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a roll of toilet paper on the toilet paper holder.
